Merge data frames

Source: R/read.R
rbind_df.Rd

Merge data frames

rbind_df(list_df)

Arguments

list_df

A list of multiple data frames with the same variables in the same order.

Value

One merged data frame with the names of the first input data frame.

Examples

rbind_df(list(iris, iris))
